  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is an action genre from a third-person perspective, Inspired by the classics of survival horror.<br><br>🗿 Runs at 60 FPS on a GTX 970 (2014) with high settings. 🗿<br><br>💻 Made in Unreal Engine 5 💻<br><br>● <strong>Satisfying combat</strong>: Battle zombies with a range of <strong>weapons</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/9b731ae76b08fc95357a4617420f1e3f.poster.avif?t=1744823589\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/9b731ae76b08fc95357a4617420f1e3f.webm?t=1744823589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/9b731ae76b08fc95357a4617420f1e3f.mp4?t=1744823589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>Classic survival horror inventory</strong>: Manage limited resources with a <strong>classic inventory system</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/1405028d4a4d92e1171a5f8aff72bef2.poster.avif?t=1744823589\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/1405028d4a4d92e1171a5f8aff72bef2.webm?t=1744823589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/1405028d4a4d92e1171a5f8aff72bef2.mp4?t=1744823589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>Progression through exploration</strong>: Find and use items to <strong>unlock new areas</strong> and advance the story.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/1787670ceb21c1821c2f36bb5f36effc.poster.avif?t=1744823589\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/1787670ceb21c1821c2f36bb5f36effc.webm?t=1744823589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/1787670ceb21c1821c2f36bb5f36effc.mp4?t=1744823589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>Open world exploration</strong>: Navigate through diverse environments like houses, a police station, sewers, and the town hall.<br>● <strong>Nostalgic soundtrack</strong>: Enjoy a familiar, classic PS1-inspired music style that enhances the atmosphere.<br>● <strong>Elevator ride</strong> for fun<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/61d842f6e688bd7ba337fc8e205469d7.poster.avif?t=1744823589\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/61d842f6e688bd7ba337fc8e205469d7.webm?t=1744823589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/61d842f6e688bd7ba337fc8e205469d7.mp4?t=1744823589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
