ysinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/1787670ceb21c1821c2f36bb5f36effc.poster.avif?t=1744823589\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/1787670ceb21c1821c2f36bb5f36effc.webm?t=1744823589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/1787670ceb21c1821c2f36bb5f36effc.mp4?t=1744823589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● <strong>Open world exploration</strong>: Navigate through diverse environments like houses, a police station, sewers, and the town hall.<br>● <strong>Nostalgic soundtrack</strong>: Enjoy a familiar, classic PS1-inspired music style that enhances the atmosphere.<br>● <strong>Elevator ride</strong> for fun<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/61d842f6e688bd7ba337fc8e205469d7.poster.avif?t=1744823589\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/61d842f6e688bd7ba337fc8e205469d7.webm?t=1744823589\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499410/extras/61d842f6e688bd7ba337fc8e205469d7.mp4?t=1744823589\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
